:Description: trimmed input for use with Alquimia interface to Amanzi
:             for sorption isotherms

:=========================== chemistry ========================================
CHEMISTRY
  PRIMARY_SPECIES
    A
    B
    C
  /

  SORPTION
    ISOTHERM_REACTIONS
      A
        TYPE LINEAR
        : Csorb = KD Caq
        DISTRIBUTION_COEFFICIENT 10.0 ! kg water/m^3 bulk
      /
      B
        TYPE LANGMUIR
        : Csorb = K Caq b / ( 1 + K Caq )
        DISTRIBUTION_COEFFICIENT 30.d0 
        LANGMUIR_B 0.1
      /
      C
        TYPE FREUNDLICH
	: Csorb = KD Caq^(1/n)
        DISTRIBUTION_COEFFICIENT 1.5
        FREUNDLICH_N  0.8 : 1/n = 1.25
      /
    /
  /

  DATABASE ./isotherms.dat
  LOG_FORMULATION
  ACTIVITY_COEFFICIENTS OFF
  OUTPUT
    All
    TOTAL
    TOTAL_SORBED
  /
END

:=========================== constraints ======================================
CONSTRAINT initial
  CONCENTRATIONS
    A  1.0e-20    T
    B  1.0e-20    T
    C  1.0e-20    T
  /
END

CONSTRAINT west
  CONCENTRATIONS
    A  1.d-3      T
    B  1.d-3      T
    C  1.d-3      T
  /
END
